TY  - JOUR
TI  - On the Global Uniqueness of Fix-Price Equilibria
AU  - Schulz, Norbert
AB  - [Fix-price equilibria à la Benassy are shown to be unique under a condition, closely related to the macroeconomic stability condition, at any price system p >> O.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jan., 1983
DB  - JSTOR
DO  - 10.2307/1912247
