TY  - JOUR
TI  - Gaussian Estimation of Structural Parameters in Higher Order Continuous Time Dynamic Models
AU  - Bergstrom, A. R.
AB  - [This paper is concerned with the efficient estimation of structural parameters in closed linear systems of higher order stochastic differential equations when the data are in discrete form and the model generally includes both stock and flow variables. A general existence and uniqueness theorem for the solution of such a system is proved and used in the rigorous derivation of exact discrete models satisfied by the various types of data. It is shown how these models can be used in the computation of various asymptotically efficient estimates obtained by the maximization of the Gaussian likelihood or approximations to it.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jan., 1983
DB  - JSTOR
